ğŸ“Œ Educational Objective

This mini project is ideal for students who want to gain a practical understanding of how linked lists work internally. Rather than relying on static data structures like arrays, the program dynamically creates nodes that are â€œlinkedâ€ to each other â€” making it a perfect illustration of self-referential classes and pointer-like behavior in Python.
